nce.\u200b<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-98297d0 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"98297d0\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>* Source : Observatoire national des violences faites aux femmes<br \/>** Source : Institut des Politiques Publiques, \u00ab\u00a0Le traitement judiciaire des violences sexuelles et conjugales en France\u00a0\u00bb, \u00e9tude publi\u00e9e en 2024 sur la p\u00e9riode 2012-2021<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ea174ef elementor-absolute elementor-widget elementor-widget-menu-anchor\" data-id=\"ea174ef\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_position&quot;:&quot;absolute&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"menu-anchor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-menu-anchor\" id=\"sans-violence\"><\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-cb172ab e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"cb172ab\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e603c8f e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"e603c8f\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-932fc8e elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"932fc8e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Une soci\u00e9t\u00e9 <span class=\"highlight-jaune\">d'\u00e9galit\u00e9<\/span><\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-